{"tid":1547603,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[核彈] [擺返啱個台] 警暴實錄（截至831）最齊版本，請廣傳！！！","createTime":"2019-09-06T17:11:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T10:34:24.000Z","uid":64171,"like":71,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"7a31e195ac019c6f950876e31e9f59f3bf4d1287","tid":1547603,"uid":64171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T17:11:30.000Z","msg":"黑警暴行轟炸！！<br />\n簡直多到氾濫！！！<br />\n<br />\n我啱啱揾到一條最齊全嘅警暴實錄，請大家攞黎傍身！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">請即刻Backup同share畀所有朋友作為黑警惡行見證！</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中文版：<a href=\"https://youtu.be/HJtNdcppvfg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FHJtNdcppvfg&d=ICpLbNdPoidNzy8g%2B0GH2r3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=69feaca5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/HJtNdcppvfg</a><br />\n<br />\n英文版：<a href=\"https://youtu.be/WWE47uUGo1E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWWE47uUGo1E&d=ICpLbNdPoidNzy8g%2B0GH2r3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=f88dca36\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/WWE47uUGo1E</a><br />\n已有中英文版！條片個備註話仲會係不久將來有<span style=\"color: red;\">德、荷 、法、日文版</span>！！！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">同藍絲老豆老母理論嘅核彈！！每日10點喺電視播一次洗佢哋腦，最好喺埋街邊放映會度不斷播放！<br />\n再配合Twitter攻勢將中港共政權下嘅popo罪行散播到全世界！！！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「若能藉著香港人近兩個多月來對暴政的抗衡，以致把全球反對共產極權統治的力量擰成一股繩，並將共產暴政拉倒，便是這一代香港人莫大的光榮。」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">驅逐共黨 光復香港！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"9bbede46c41160a345957aec62e91a27817a1864","tid":1547603,"uid":64171,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T17:12:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/27/Wr0hsj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F27%2FWr0hsj.gif&h=b79bcc9b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"19785c412615d915036b77102ac19a187c7461cd","tid":1547603,"uid":228354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T17:12:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b42df942d9e763e54942d862f679ecf0dddb215b","tid":1547603,"uid":64171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T17:14:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dafd3352258717d426ef82b19d3c6f07d9424b12","tid":1547603,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T17:14:48.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打!"},{"pid":"fbd45a9040eb9fc3862c3857da60f96b0ea19923","tid":1547603,"uid":64171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T17:14:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji