;\">德、荷 、法、日文版</span>！！！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">同藍絲老豆老母理論嘅核彈！！每日10點喺電視播一次洗佢哋腦，最好喺埋街邊放映會度不斷播放！<br />\n再配合Twitter攻勢將中港共政權下嘅popo罪行散播到全世界！！！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「若能藉著香港人近兩個多月來對暴政的抗衡，以致把全球反對共產極權統治的力量擰成一股繩，並將共產暴政拉倒，便是這一代香港人莫大的光榮。」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">驅逐共黨 光復香港！！！</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T00:53:20.000Z","msg":"Push ar"},{"pid":"3342a08869d70e4b38ce94fa66115955525b01c0","tid":1547603,"uid":227405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T01:54:43.000Z","msg":"辛苦你"},{"pid":"afc13ca636086d8d33ed95c3ca85d5d6183fa76e","tid":1547603,"uid":26876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T01:55:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"40a21da369a6b95c209711a1a4404ef99fea7ffa","tid":1547603,"uid":92347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T01:58:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b15c08a49475ac7eafa5af70c037d8249bdfa67e","tid":1547603,"uid":275979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T02:03:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97cbe2f07baffdfa10a7c9284703da48128202cd","tid":1547603,"uid":254246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T02